text: Stanisław Dulias (12 April 1939 – 17 November 2020) was a Polish politician and economist. Dulias was born in Zbarazh, Poland. He was a member of the Sejm from 2001 to 2005. Dulias died on 17 November 2020 of COVID-19 in Mysłowice, Poland at the age of 81. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Polish politicians Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Poland Category:Polish scientists Category:Polish economists
